                <div class="about-section">
                    <h2>Our Commitment</h2>
                    <p>We're committed to maintaining RateFlow as a free public service. As we grow, we'll continue to:</p>
                    <ul class="features-list">
                        <li>Add more currencies and financial tools</li>
